Framed Prints

Introducing the exquisite Framed Print from Media Storehouse's historic collection, featuring the iconic photograph "Historic parade in Piazza d'Armi in Florence for the wedding of King Umberto I and Margherita" by Fratelli Alinari. This stunning image captures the grandeur and elegance of the royal wedding procession, which took place in Turin on April 22, 1868. The photograph was captured just days after the wedding, on May 2, 1868, and beautifully preserves a moment in time from Italy's rich history. This Framed Print is not only a beautiful addition to your home or office, but also a testament to the masterful photography of the Fratelli Alinari. Bring a piece of history into your space with this timeless Framed Print.

Photo Prints

Step back in time with this stunning historic photograph from the Alinari Archives. Witness the grandeur of the past as you gaze upon the "Historic parade in Piazza d'Armi in Florence for the wedding of King Umberto I and Margherita," taken on May 2, 1868. This exquisite image captures the elaborate procession through the heart of Florence as the city celebrated the royal wedding between Italy's first king and queen. Add this beautiful piece of history to your home or office with our premium quality Media Storehouse Photographic Print, expertly crafted to preserve the rich details and authenticity of this Alinari Fratelli masterpiece.

Jigsaw Puzzles

Step back in time with our exquisite jigsaw puzzle from Media Storehouse - Historic Parade in Piazza d'Armi, Florence. This beautiful puzzle features an iconic photograph by Fratelli Alinari, capturing the grand historic parade in Florence for the wedding of King Umberto I and Queen Margherita of Savoy, which took place in Turin on April 22, 1868. The photograph, taken on February 5, 1868, showcases the grandeur and opulence of the royal wedding procession. Immerse yourself in this piece of history and enjoy the challenge of piecing together this stunning image, perfect for puzzle enthusiasts and history buffs alike.
